 - Use CONFIG_FUNCTION_GRAPH_TRACER to control fgraph_ret_regs definition

v9:
 - Fix stack pointer align issues
 - Update the commit message

v8:
 - Modify the control range of CONFIG_HAVE_FUNCTION_GRAPH_RETVAL
